  How many hours did the worker work during the pay period?
<% end %>

<% content_for :hint do %>
This includes: 

+  any time your employee was at work and needed to be available for work 
+  any time spent travelling in connection with work (for example, travelling to a training course or between work locations)

If you have not reimbursed the worker for something they bought for work (for example tools or a uniform) then you need to deduct the cost from amount they were paid. 

^Do not include overtime or time taken to travel to their normal workplace.
<% end %>

